                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_fælaxs" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>fælaxs</orth></form><sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>стертый</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>rubbed off</q></tr></sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>осунувшийся</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>haggard</q></tr></sense><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>исхудалый</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>gaunt</q></tr></sense></sense><exampleGrp><example><quote>mæ cævæg ysfælaxs ī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>моя коса стерлась</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>my scythe became worn out</q></tr></example><example><quote>mæj ysfælaxs ī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>месяц стал тонким (на ущербе)</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>the moon has become thin</q></tr></example><example><quote>nizæj ysfælaxs ī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>от болезни он осунулся</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>he got thinner from illness</q></tr></example></exampleGrp><exampleGrp><example><quote>mæ cævæg ysfælaxs ī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>моя коса стерлась</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>my scythe became worn out</q></tr></example><example><quote>mæj ysfælaxs ī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>месяц стал тонким (на ущербе)</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>the moon has become thin</q></tr></example><example><quote>nizæj ysfælaxs ī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>от болезни он осунулся</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>he got thinner from illness</q></tr></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, усеченное %i*fæl-a-xsyd%i из %i*pari-ā-xšita-%i. Восстанавливаемое %i*xsyd%i | %i*xsid%i представляет прош. причастие от глагола %ixši-%i, наличного в <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ixsyjyn"/> ‘стираться’, ‘изнашиваться’, ‘истощаться’. Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>kṣi-</w> <gloss><q>идти на убыль</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>чахнуть</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>истощаться</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>kṣita-</w> <gloss><q>истощенный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>kṣīṇa-</w> <gloss><q>стертый</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>тонкий (например, месяц на ущербе)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>осунувшийся</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>исхудалый</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>xsī-</w> <gloss><q>истощение</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/> <gloss><q>нищета</q></gloss></mentioned>, . Ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ixsyjyn"/> и <ref type="xr" target="#entry_xsynyn"/>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Probably, a shortened %i*fæl-a-xsyd%i from %i*pari-ā-xšita-%i. A reconstructed form %i*xsyd%i | %i*xsid%i is a past participle from the verb %ixši-%i, which is present in <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ixsyjyn"/> ‘wipe off’, ‘rub off’, ‘run low’. Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>kṣi-</w> <gloss><q>decline</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>wither</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>run low</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>kṣita-</w> <gloss><q>exhausted</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w>kṣīṇa-</w> <gloss><q>rubbed off</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>thin (e.g., a waning moon)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>haggard</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>gaunt</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/> <w>xsī-</w> <gloss><q>exhaustion</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="ae"><w/> <gloss><q>poverty</q></gloss></mentioned>, . Cf. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ixsyjyn"/> and <ref type="xr" target="#entry_xsynyn"/>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>